# /croq-tune — Kernel Tuning Dispatcher

When the user say "/croq-tune":

1. Read `.cursor/skills/cursor-croq-tune/SKILL.md` — the Cursor-only tuning entrypoint
2. Parse the user's `dsl`, `dtype`, optional `shape_key`, any `--model`, any `--task-uid`, and any stated round-budget language from their message
3. Read the matching `.cursor/skills/cursor-croq-dsl-<dsl>/SKILL.md` for the Cursor-side DSL entrypoint
4. Follow the protocol in `.cursor/skills/cursor-croq-tune/SKILL.md` exactly
